Class AggregateConvexHullRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gisfederal.gpudb.protocol.AggregateConvexHullRequest

    public class AggregateConvexHullRequest
extends Object
implements org.apache.avro.generic.IndexedRecord
    A set of parameters for GPUdb.aggregateConvexHull(AggregateConvexHullRequest).

    Calculates and returns the convex hull for the values in a table specified by tableName.
